<h4 class="pdoc-member-header" id="StoreState-retentionPeriod">
<a class="pdoc-child-name" href="https://github.com/pulumi/pulumi-alicloud/blob/{{< param git_sha >}}/sdk/nodejs/log/store.ts#L151">property <b>retentionPeriod</b></a>
